{"type": "article", "id": 34983, "title": "用废纸做的笔，还能削出漂亮的花｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-28T23:08:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 17302, "name": "Layer"}, {"id": 35283, "name": "NOOMOON"}, {"id": 35284, "name": "holi"}, {"id": 35285, "name": "TRINUS"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 148, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161128175212BHUsZjLd9Af5DNXc.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>LABB by NOOMOON &amp; Layer</h3><p>曾经推出过 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27425.html\">3D 打印轮椅</a>的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://layerdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Layer</a> 为瑞士品牌 NOOMOON 设计了一款佩戴起来非常方便的 Apple Watch 表带 LABB，它采用一种名叫 FKM 的材料制成，摸起来相当柔软而且具有防水功能。和常见的表带不同，LABB 不通过额外的扣子进行固定。只需要将两边互补的纹理图案扣上，它就能契合用户的手腕迅速戴好，单手也可以完成操作。LABB 提供多种颜色可选，不用担心表带和装扮不搭。美中不足的是，它目前只支持 42 毫米的表壳。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1706210184/noomoon-add-the-swiss-touch-to-your-apple-watch\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 57 瑞士法郎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175406AGyS0qwRHoFBMPOp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281754063NV0Ax86z9thYQbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175406hsfPANpGzobY9OJF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783824\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175406QabSZ371PJGLUfAr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769118\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175406WvBps7TbxMld6Z5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769118\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175407AeI0ibKpFEqy6kSD.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.133824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bonjour by holi</h3><p>受到影片《her》的启发，法国初创公司 <a href=\"https://www.holi.io/fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">holi</a> 经过两年时间研发了一款名为 Bonjour 的智能闹钟，这个采用语音控制的设备可以通过学习人们的作息来充当个人助手，和片中的 AI 还有些相似。闹钟本身的造型相当简洁，一块圆形的屏幕取代了常见的钟面。除了初始设置是通过配套应用完成之外，日常控制都是通过语音进行（目前仅支持英语和法语）。Bonjour 可以通过和日历、地图、信息以及 Uber 等应用的数据互通，为用户提供相应的提醒。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1450781303/bonjour-smart-alarm-clock-with-artificial-intellig\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低为 119 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175325BQn8bfs9hRS4zEud.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744118\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175324HcEdrq4mioVfXRLI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175325d14iajMuWyNL506H.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779412\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281753254cvmKkFRzNwxrSMq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175324LPNRV2jhqbputvJ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485294\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>花色铅笔 by TRINUS</h3><p>在经历了一年半的研发之后，日本设计公司 <a href=\"https://trinus.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TRINUS</a> 推出了一款能让人削出花朵的铅笔。正如其名，这套花色铅笔的灵感源自日本文化中常见的五种花朵，并且和它们的颜色一一对应，淡雅的颜色和五角形的白色包装搭配看上去也相当契合。除了漂亮的造型之外，花色铅笔也相当注重环保的制作理念，围绕着笔芯的并不是木料，而是回收来的废纸。你可以通过<a href=\"https://trinus.jp/developments/1?topic=40\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，一组的价格为 1600 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175308AY3o6JqnVR1WhG4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281753085lzkCbscIVWRp7FQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175308x7uERAQBKGhbHDZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175308hPxvc2lSNLkpRgT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175308wOUvj3zp0kWgifoQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>HAENG</h3><p>像珠宝手链一样，吊灯也可以订制了。<a href=\"https://haeng.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HAENG</a> 是一个成立于 2015 年的丹麦品牌，专门经营模块化的吊灯。串在灯泡上的各类几何形组件均由软木塞和木块制成，旗下的成品线分为 Basic 和 HAENG 两种，不同之处在于后者的组件还包裹上了五颜六色的毛毡。你可以通过<a href=\"https://haeng.dk/collections/all\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些吊灯，售价从 1749 丹麦克朗起。如果你最近前往哥本哈根的话，还可以去拜访 HAENG 新近开张的概念店，订制一款独一无二的吊灯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194115Q9UyEJudTKg0nGlz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194116tD8dTuMEI65n4iFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194115UJKSowXZpsdgYOCL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.530864\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281941156SqNDUQhKmeVaOu9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.530864\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016112819411626tfb8DpnHzgNKAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.530864\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194116rPAE1ulhvZoi5D2q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Birdhouse by Sourgrassbuilt</h3><p>如果小鸟也有属于自己的屋子，会是什么样的呢？美国家居装饰品牌 Sourgrassbuilt 根据人类的住宅打造了一批迷你又舒适的鸟屋，这些漂亮的小房子不仅有可供鸟儿停歇的小圆柱，还有种着植物的墙面和花园，看起来非常可爱。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.sourgrassbuilt.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买到这些鸟屋，售价从 149.99 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194138jVnfHJE1qgARZsm9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194138yQKlvzmt2Gos8p0J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194139vLcAE8wnZ9rDeFqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128194138RZfUrH8YENqxKMzI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Turmeon Honey</h3><p>继<a href=\"http://tapasmagazine.com/turmeon-it-is-not-just-good-vermouth-it-is-also-a-great-packaging/\" rel=\"nofollow\">改吃心脏的吃豆人</a>和跃起的海豚之后，西班牙味美思酒品牌 <a href=\"http://www.turmeon.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Turmeon</a> 又为旗下的新产品 Turmeon Honey 这一世界首款加入蜂蜜调味的味美思酒设计了有着动态效果的包装。在多个图层堆叠的作用下，转动瓶身时标签上的蜜蜂也会随之挥动翅膀。契合蜂蜜这一元素，包装上的文字也采用了橙黑两色的搭配。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175250yjfCO8RHTLe1kAp2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175251IWkimupG4Z05rYsx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175250Jdp6fNnClXW75QU9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128175250gsQPlHR7xAU6pj59.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.941875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}